---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import dashboard from '../assets/images/dashboard.jpg';
import heroBg from '../assets/images/nina-sembrando.png';
---

<section
  class="relative mb-[28vw] flex w-full items-center justify-center overflow-hidden pb-24 sm:pb-32 md:mb-[18vw] md:pb-44 lg:mb-[10vw] lg:pb-0 xl:mb-[13vw] 2xl:mb-60"
  id="home"
>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <Image
      src={heroBg}
      alt=""
      class="h-full w-full object-cover object-[center_40%]"
      fetchpriority="high"
      loading="eager"
    />
    <div class="hero-bg-overlay absolute inset-0" style="opacity: 0.85;"></div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="relative z-10 flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-center pt-16 text-center md:w-[50rem] md:pt-16 lg:pt-20 xl:w-[56.25rem]"
  >
    <div class="hero-fade-in" style="--delay: 0s">
      <span class="block-subtitle mt-16 mb-6 block text-[0.65rem] sm:mt-32 sm:text-xs">
        COMUNIDAD, NATURALEZA Y APRENDISAJE VIVO
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-fade-in mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4" style="--delay: 0.05s">
      <h1
        class="xs:text-4xl text-[1.7rem] leading-[1.1] font-bold tracking-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl"
      >
        <span class="text-heroText">Sembramos hoy la nueva</span><br />
        <span class="text-heroText">humanidad del mañana</span>
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-fade-in" style="--delay: 0.1s">
      <p
        class="text-secondaryText mx-auto mt-7 max-w-2xl px-4 text-sm leading-relaxed sm:text-base"
      >
      En Eco Escuela Ser creemos que cada niño merece crecer en un espacio donde su esencia sea respetada, su curiosidad sea celebrada y su conexión con la naturaleza sea profunda. Ofrecemos una educación integral basada en metodologías innovadoras que despiertan el potencial único de cada ser humano.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-fade-in" style="--delay: 0.15s">
      <div class="mt-10 mb-24 flex flex-col justify-center gap-2 sm:mb-40 sm:flex-row">
        <button
          class="contained-button mr-0 mb-2 h-12 w-72 text-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(109,62,6,0.4)] sm:mr-2 sm:mb-0 sm:w-44 lg:mr-3"
          data-open-modal
          aria-label="Get started"
        >
          Admisión 2026
        </button>
        <button
          class="text-primaryText bg-bgDark2 hover:bg-bgDark3 border-primaryColor flex h-12 w-72 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-solid text-sm font-bold transition sm:w-44"
          data-open-modal
          aria-label="Live demo"
        >
          Propuesta
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-20 flex w-screen justify-center">
      <div
        class="hero-fade-in image-glow-border absolute z-10 mx-auto w-4/5 rounded-xl lg:top-6 xl:top-0 2xl:w-[75rem]"
        style="--delay: 0.15s; opacity: 0.005"
      >
        <Image
          src={dashboard}
          alt="Dashboard image"
          class="main-border-gray w-full rounded-xl"
          fetchpriority="high"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-xl bg-black/10"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative flex w-screen justify-center">
      <div class="shape-divider-bottom-1665343298 mt-4 hidden sm:mt-16 md:mt-52 lg:block">
        <svg
          data-name="Layer 1"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 1200 120"
          preserveAspectRatio="none"
          class="bg-bgDark2"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path d="M1200 0L0 0 598.97 114.72 1200 0z" class="shape-fill bg-bgDark1 fill-bgDark1"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-bg-overlay {
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(77 108 31 / 0.3) 0%, transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        rgb(28 39 11 / 0.92) 0%,
        rgb(40 56 16 / 0.78) 38%,
        rgb(28 39 11 / 0.88) 72%,
        rgb(28 39 11) 100%
      );
  }

  .hero-fade-in {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(10px);
    animation: heroFadeIn 0.5s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: var(--delay);
  }

  @keyframes heroFadeIn {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
